        <div style="font-weight:800;font-size:1rem;color:#92400e;margin-bottom:8px;">🏢 Why Offline Games Come First at Bhāva Tech</div>
        <div style="font-size:0.87rem;color:#78350f;line-height:1.7;">Physical games engage motor memory, tactile senses, and direct human interaction — creating deeper neural encoding than screens alone. Our <strong>office and lab in Vizag</strong> exist specifically to provide this environment: a focused, screen-free space where children experience the joy of thinking with their hands and minds — together.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ONLINE PANEL -->
