      <div class="bgt-card" style="border-top:4px solid #06b6d4;">
        <span class="bgt-icon">🎮</span><h4>Bhaava Brain Quest</h4>
        <p>IQ &amp; pattern training in a gamified quest format — available globally via browser.</p>
      </div>
      
	  <div class="bgt-card" style="border-top:4px solid #7c3aed;">
        <span class="bgt-icon">🧩</span><h4>MindSpark IQ</h4>
        <p>Progressive difficulty puzzles that adapt to the
		child's current cognitive level.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bgt-card" style="border-top:4px solid #059669;">
        <span class="bgt-icon">🌿</span><h4>Brain Garden</h4>
        <p>Memory cultivation — grow your memory garden by correctly recalling sequences.</p>
